Slučajno sam prekinuo.
U redu?

00:27:39.406 --> 00:27:41.440
Dejvide, ostani miran.
Možeš ti to.

00:27:42.597 --> 00:27:43.953
Samo me slušaj.

00:27:57.614 --> 00:27:59.625
Keli, mogao bih te
slušati celi dan,

00:27:59.750 --> 00:28:01.784
