nastavim s pljačkom.

00:28:10.189 --> 00:28:13.777
Gente, prošlo je već dva sata!
Zašto ti tako dugo treba?

00:28:13.944 --> 00:28:15.226
Gotovo!

00:28:16.384 --> 00:28:18.313
U redu, to je sve.
Još samo kamere.

00:29:19.846 --> 00:29:20.971
Ne!

00:29:21.640 --> 00:29:22.807
Ne!

00:29:26.812 --> 00:29:28.146
Zaključan sam!

00:29:52.965 --> 00:29:54.508
Prokleti kukovi!

00:30:37.658 --> 00:30:40.285
Bože, ne mogu da zakočim!

00:30:40.598 --> 00:30:42.256
Šta to radi?

00:30:54.050 --> 00:30:55.447
Pomagajte!

00:30:56.802 --> 00:30:58.534
Pazite da vam ne vidi lica!

00:30:59.221 --> 00:31:01.452
Do đavola, idiote!
Šta to radiš?

00:31:01.577 --> 00:31:03.247
Otključaj vrata.
- Zaglavio sam se!

00:31:03.372 --> 00:31:07.042
Proveri s druge strane.
Idiote, sleteo si pravo u jarak!

00:31:07.730 --> 00:31:09.170
I ova su isto zaključana.

00:31:09.295 --> 00:31:11.047
Kaže da su i ova zaključana!

